name: myTino
tag_list: online-outsourcing, graphics-&-design, china-business-consulting, web-development, software-development, freelance, freelancer
overview:
myTino.com is an outsourcing network that allows Professionals and SMEs to outsource online to China.

‘Buyers’ can reduce costs by outsourcing to professionals in emerging markets such as India and China. Likewise, ‘Providers’ can find lucrative work opportunities by bidding for jobs posted by individuals and organizations in developed nations from America and Europe.

offices.address1: 14th Floor, East Software Park, 90 Wensan Road
